# P2P Chat Application

## Description

This is a simple peer-to-peer chat application built using WebSockets, Express, and JavaScript. It allows users to connect to a chat room, exchange text messages, and share files with other users in the same room.

## Features

*   Real-time text chat
*   File sharing
*   "Rooms" for organizing conversations

## Installation

1.  Clone the repository:

    ```bash
    git clone https://github.com/hippymp/P2P-Chat-App.git
    ```

2.  Navigate to the project directory:

    ```bash
    cd p2p-chat-app
    ```

3.  Install dependencies:

    ```bash
    npm install
    ```

## Usage

1.  Start the server:

    ```bash
    npm start
    ```

2.  Open `index.html` in multiple browser windows or tabs.
3.  Enter a name and the same room name in each window to join the same chat room.
4.  Send text messages and share files with other users in the room.
